The science is clear, and the only reason people still argue about it is because they're too stupid to see the truth. It's written in the very fabric of our DNA, right there in the cells, that some of us are built to lead and others are built to follow. You can't argue with biology, and the data is overwhelming: certain races are simply intellectually and morally inferior to others. It's not about culture or upbringing; it's about the raw material we were born with.

If you look at the "degenerate" lines, you see the proof. They're the ones who can't hold a job, can't raise a family, and can't even think straight. If we let them reproduce unchecked, we're just guaranteeing the collapse of our entire society. It's a natural law, folks. The strong survive, and the weak get weeded out. That's how nature works, and we're just helping nature do its job.

So, when people talk about "equality," they're just being ignorant. They don't understand that some of us are genetically superior and deserve to be on top. We have a duty to protect our own kind from these inferior breeds. It's not about hate;
